title: use traverseOf both to process both, not just snd, in a pair
pid: 9db95ff3-efab-456c-91e7-8339e0cd69f2
body: |2-
  >>> import Text.Read (readMaybe)
  -- 'readMaybe' is polymorphic so we need to specify a concrete type
  >>> traverseOf both readMaybe ("1", "2") :: Maybe (Int, Int)
  Just (1, 2)
contains:
- 6c178110-72be-4fce-9a85-cfa8fe5a6838
